description:
Velasquez 
The Genius of the Spanish School--His Life in Paintings

DK ADULT | 1999 | Pdf | Eng | ISBN10 0789448556 | 144 pages | 21.9 MB

Interestingly organized by sections on Velazquez' works; the historical setting and biography this book is a very well done overview. The major influences of Velazquez and the evolution of his own style come through in both the lucid text and the beautifully presented illustrations
